WEBVTT

1.1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.258
Before you sell a single kitchen, you need to know what Magppie actually is.

1.2
00:00:05.258 --> 00:00:10.516
Here's the surprise — it isn't a kitchen company.

2.1
00:00:10.516 --> 00:00:15.527
Our mission is to transform ordinary homes into wellness homes.

2.2
00:00:15.527 --> 00:00:20.538
Spaces that keep you, your family, and the planet safe.

2.3
00:00:20.538 --> 00:00:25.549
Magppie is a Wellness Movement.

2.4
00:00:25.549 --> 00:00:30.560
We don't sell kitchens — we sell health, safety, and twenty-five years of peace of mind.

3.1
00:00:30.560 --> 00:00:36.177
There is exactly one version of the company story, and it never changes.

3.2
00:00:36.177 --> 00:00:41.794
Magppie Group has been in business for over fifty years.

3.3
00:00:41.794 --> 00:00:47.411
For the past twenty-plus years, we have been creating kitchens and wardrobes.

3.4
00:00:47.411 --> 00:00:53.028
And our first SilverStone kitchen gave us nine-plus years of real-world performance validation.

4.1
00:00:53.028 --> 00:00:57.365
Never say we're thirty-five or forty years old.

4.2
00:00:57.365 --> 00:01:01.703
Never open with stainless steel.

4.3
00:01:01.703 --> 00:01:06.040
One story, one order: group heritage, kitchens, SilverStone.

5.1
00:01:06.040 --> 00:01:11.999
Through twenty years of building kitchens we kept seeing the same failures — termites, mould, water sagging, and formaldehyde from plywood and MDF.

5.2
00:01:11.999 --> 00:01:17.958
The industry kept selling finishes.

5.3
00:01:17.958 --> 00:01:23.917
Nobody fixed the material.

5.4
00:01:23.917 --> 00:01:29.876
That gap is why SilverStone exists — and it's the story every sales conversation is anchored on.

6.1
00:01:29.876 --> 00:01:36.520
Before the quiz, write these down.

6.2
00:01:36.520 --> 00:01:43.164
One — the mission: transform ordinary homes into wellness homes.

6.3
00:01:43.164 --> 00:01:49.808
Two — Magppie is a wellness movement: we sell health, safety, and twenty-five years of peace of mind.

6.4
00:01:49.808 --> 00:01:56.452
Three — one story, one order: fifty-plus years of group heritage, twenty-plus in kitchens, nine-plus of SilverStone.

6.5
00:01:56.452 --> 00:02:03.096
Four — never say thirty-five or forty years old, and never open with stainless steel.

7.1
00:02:03.096 --> 00:02:07.996
Learn the story word for word — then take the quiz.

